#: ../../H/ha-ha-only-serious.rst:5
msgid "ha ha only serious"
msgstr "ha ha only serious"

#: ../../H/ha-ha-only-serious.rst:7
msgid ""
"[from SF fandom, orig. as mutation of HHOK, ‘Ha Ha Only Kidding’] A phrase "
"(often seen abbreviated as HHOS) that aptly captures the flavor of much "
"hacker discourse. Applied especially to parodies, absurdities, and ironic "
"jokes that are both intended and perceived to contain a possibly disquieting"
" amount of truth, or truths that are constructed on in-joke and self-parody."
" This lexicon contains many examples of ha-ha-only-serious in both form and "
"content. Indeed, the entirety of hacker culture is often perceived as ha-ha-"
"only-serious by hackers themselves; to take it either too lightly or too "
"seriously marks a person as an outsider, a :ref:`wannabee`\\, or in "
":ref:`larval-stage`\\. For further enlightenment on this subject, consult "
"any Zen master. See also :ref:`hacker-humor`\\, and :ref:`koan`\\."
msgstr ""
"[SFファンダムより、元はHHOK‘Ha Ha Only "
"Kidding’の変異として]多くのハッカーの談話の風味を見事に捉えた言い回し(しばしばHHOSと略される)。特に、おそらく不安にさせるほどの量の真実、あるいは内輪のジョークや自己パロディの上に構築された真実を、意図的に含み、かつそう受け取られるパロディ、不条理、皮肉なジョークに適用される。この用語集には、形式と内容の両面でha-"
"ha-only-seriousの例が多数含まれている。実際、ハッカー文化全体がしばしばハッカー自身によってha-ha-only-"
"seriousと受け取られる。それを軽く受け取りすぎても真剣に受け取りすぎても、その人はよそ者、\\ :ref:`wannabee`\\ 、あるいは\\"
" :ref:`larval-stage`\\ にあると見なされる。この主題についてさらに啓発を得るには、どの禅師にでも尋ねるとよい。\\ "
":ref:`hacker-humor`\\ 、および\\ :ref:`koan`\\ も参照。"
